#~ "&kmail; accesses <application>PGP</application>/<application>GnuPG</"
#~ "application> synchronously, &ie; it blocks while <application>PGP</"
#~ "application>/<application>GnuPG</application> works. This means that you "
#~ "might want to disable automatic retrieval of unknown keys from a "
